node.title: Body found inside submerged ute in Lake Dunstan near Queenstown
node.description: Police started a search on Tuesday afternoon and found the vehicle's sole occupant.
node.content: ["A body has been found inside a submerged ute in Lake Dunstan near Queenstown on Tuesday.", "Emergency services were called to the crash on Monday night after a ute towing a trailer plunged into the water.", "Police say the national dive squad started a search early Tuesday afternoon and they have now recovered the vehicle's sole occupant.", "\"Enquiries in relation to the death on behalf of the coroner are underway,\" a police spokesperson says.", "\"The removal of the vehicle and trailer is currently being completed.\"", "Police say no further details will be provided until an official identification process has been completed."]
